      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BAREFOOT ZULU (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (27.57) in a Grade 4/5 at Horsham. Solid record at the distance winning eight races. Form from his last run is proving strong. Has ability and is a key runner. PAW OSWALD (2) was well in the market last time but only managed fifth (30.44), beaten 8 lengths. Finished second the start before. Goes very well from this draw with five wins and two minor placings from seven starts. Leading chance. TENACIOUS TALKER (5) boasts a strong record this journey here with four wins and three minors from nine tries. In the money last time at this track (30.01) in a Grade 5, finishing a 1.5 lengths third. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. ZIPPING SNEAD (3) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
